/Pattern2 {PatternBgnd KeepColor Pat2 setpattern} bind def
/Pattern3 {PatternBgnd KeepColor Pat3 setpattern} bind def
/Pattern4 {PatternBgnd KeepColor Landscape {Pat5} {Pat4} ifelse setpattern} bind def
